Mexico Remittances at $1.87 Billion in April, Central Bank Says

-- B y   C r a y t o n   H a r r i s o n
-- 
2011-06-01T14:03:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-01/mexico-remittances-at-1-87-billion-in-april-central-bank-says.html
Mexican remittances rose 4.7 percent
in April from a year earlier to $1.87 billion, the central bank
said today on its website. That matches the median estimate in a
Bloomberg survey of seven analysts compiled by Bloomberg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Crayton Harrison in Mexico City at 
 tharrison5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
